%p
  Bookmark this page and visit it often to keep track of news about RbMU,
  including new calls for participation, events with guest speakers, or
  study sessions with our alumni and staff.  You can also keep track of
  what's going on at RMU by following the #RbMU hash tag on twitter,
  subscribing to the
  = link_to "rmu-talk mailing list", "http://groups.google.com/group/rmu-talk"
  , or to the
  = link_to "RSS feed",
    :controller => "public", :action => "changelog", :format => "rss"
  for this page.

#announcements
  - @announcements.each do |announcement|
    .announcement
      .title
        = link_to announcement.title, "/changelog/#{announcement.slug}"
        .info
          .author= announcement.author.name
          .posted_date= announcement.created_at.to_date
      .body= md(announcement.body)


= will_paginate @announcements